Trade/Device Name(s): PRECICHEK NS-101 POCT Professional Blood Glucose Monitoring System
PRECICHEK KP Blood Glucose Test Strip
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): PRECICHEK NS-101 POCT Professional Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for PRECICHEK NS-101 POCT Professional Blood Glucose Monitoring System for measuring glucose in whole blood using an electrochemical biosensor.
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary, venous, and arterial whole blood samples by healthcare professionals in clinical settings as an aid to monitor diabetes control; not for diagnosis, screening, or neonatal use.
